data.description: Discover elegance in this 3,320 sq ft residence boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Ascend to the upper level, where an expansive bonus room await, providing versatility and ample space. a second family room adds to the allure, creating a home that seamlessly blends comfort and functionality. Immerse yourself in the warmth of the fireplace, unwind in the heated sunroom and indulge in the luxury of a sparkling pool. Your dream home awaits.
